    <div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-8 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
    <p class="gem-c-title__context">
      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Get access to CHIEF for transitional simplified procedures
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">You’ll need to get access to CHIEF if you’re making declarations yourself for goods imported using transitional simplified procedures after Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

